    "description": "<strong>Vectic</strong>: The motorsport of the future. <br><br>Every year the Vectic League draws millions of fans from all over the world. <br>This season you will not be one of them. <br>This season you will be a contender. <br>Race with skill, speed and daring to claim your place in the record books as a Vectic legend. <br><br>Vectic uses a turn based system to bring you a new racing experience. To be victorious is to be not only the fastest but also the smartest. Gain the edge by picking your way through obstacles, optimising corners or landing the perfect hit with a laser beam. Prevail on over 40 hand built race tracks.<br><br>The stakes have been raised even higher with new content for the Boosted Edition:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Freeform colour customisation<br></li><li> Expanded soundtrack with track selection<br></li><li> All new secret options for added replayability</li></ul>",
